# Approach
Using DP and take reference form previous normal fibonacci question.
Example :Here if we have to find tribonacci of 4 then we have to break it in form of 1+3 i.e 4. so here we first take the base condition and do n=n-3 as we have to convert it in form of Tn+3 = Tn + Tn+1 + Tn+2 for n >= 0. so we do n=n-3 and store our answer in dp
then return dp[n].

